ygData.messageBody:
Ok im just about to leave work now, ill be online in about an hour in a half
ill be in and around the oasis. For the sheild ill take 50 plat or so. Maybe
some Bronze plate if you got any for trade. Anyways talk to you in a bit in
game.

Rayne
